        Creates a new descriptor for a numeric (double) setting.
        Parameters:
        id - the id, which should resemble the name of the setting
        name - the name of the setting
        description - short description
        min - the minimum value (inclusive), default is Long.MIN_VALUE
        max - the maximum value (inclusive), default is Long.MAX_VALUE
